{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1969,"month":2,"day":10}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"“拥军篮”（唱词）","authors":["四五一二部队毛泽东思想宣传队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳一出金灿灿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒万丈照山川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想大普及，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光雨露润心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动人事迹千千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥军爱民有新篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话说六连荣誉室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈列一只“拥军篮”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这只篮儿很平常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面尽是窟窿眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里边是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦菜、瓜秧、黄麻叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一件烂布衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问这是咋回事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听咱从头表一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六连去年四月间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支农来到洪家湾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命红旗高高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把毛泽东思想来宣传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民一起抓革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民一道促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民同批刘少奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民同办学习班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同战斗情意重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼水深情心相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里有位李大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她家住在村东南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说部队要转移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘心里热浪翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队这次进村来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把毛泽东思想送到咱心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了革命和生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里来，雨里去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕劳累和艰难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人要走送些啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘心里细盘算："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“千万不要忘记阶级斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士都是年轻人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没受过旧社会苦和寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲讲吃人的旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级仇恨记心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死保卫毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋陷阵永向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘屋里开了柜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取出礼物整两件："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去用的要饭篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三代穿的烂布衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拿破篮和破衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘心头怒火燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是贫下中农的血泪账，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语说不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘手拿礼物到部队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见锣鼓闹喧天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘正要把话讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位贫农大爷到跟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）“他大娘，你等一下。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大爷在“拥军篮”里放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了些苦苦菜、地瓜秧、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄麻叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们心是一个样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们一块把礼献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员双手接过“拥军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含着热泪把话谈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）同志们，大家看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农吃的是这种饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿的是这样的破布衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叛徒、内奸、工贼刘少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想叫咱们把苦受二遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们要批臭刘少奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫他永世不得把身翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士铁拳紧紧握，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个心中怒火燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“坚决打倒刘少奇！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵口号冲云天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民热爱子弟兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送上珍贵的“拥军篮”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争永不忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永向前。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}